        "heading_size": "title-sm",
        "heading_alignment": "text-left md:items-end md:flex-row",
        "heading_tag": "h2",
        "subheading": "",
        "description": "<p>Hauler is the first cargo-focused Ebike from Heybike. Designed for hauling goods, groceries,family members, and more, the Hauler is ideal for the city-slicker, country-sider, and everyone in between. The Hauler is made for hauling; from farming produce, to carting around the kids, to Postmates delivery drivers, the large carrying capacity gives riders the ability to haul everything they need.<br/>A powerful, 1400W motor gives Hauler riders the ability to do more than stick to the daily commute or grocery run. With the Hauler, riders have the potential to take on those interesting side roads, explore parks near and far, or grab coffee from a cafe that's just out of walking distance. For any road or route, all things are possible.</p>",
