            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "video_url": "",
            "description": "",
            "enable_video_autoplay": false,
            "enable_video_looping": false,
            "heading": "Powerful Motor",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>The powerful 750W rear hub motor, with a peak output of 1400W and an impressive 80Nm of torque, delivers exceptional power and acceleration to make transportation with cargo a breeze. Additionally, the Shimano 7-speed gear shift system allows you to find the optimal speed for any journey.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_WbeTB7": {
