            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>Hauler's comfortable saddle must be your favorite. Its breathable hollow design enhances air circulation, reducing pressure on the hips and discomfort from sweating. Additionally, the dual spring damper balls provide exceptional elasticity, offering superior hip protection and a remarkably comfortable ride.</p>",
